- gfs2: Fix duplicate should_fault_in_pages() call (Andreas Gruenbacher) [RHEL-130505]
- smc: Use __sk_dst_get() and dst_dev_rcu() in smc_clc_prfx_match(). (Mete Durlu) [RHEL-130012] {CVE-2025-40168}

